import React from 'react';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import { Button, Flex, Stack, Box } from '@chakra-ui/core'
import customTheme from '../../theme';

function Home() {
  return (
    <Box w={width || '350px'} marginTop="15px" rounded="md" bg={customTheme.themeColors[200]} boxShadow="xl">
    <Flex w="100%" padding="10" flexDirection="column" justifyContent="center" alignContent="center">
    <Stack spacing={8} p={8}>
    <Link to="/emergency">
    <Button w="100%" size="lg" bg={customTheme.themeColors[500]}>Emergency</Button>
   </Link>
   <Link to="/adopt">
      <Button w="100%" size="lg" bg={customTheme.themeColors[500]}>Adopta</Button>
   </Link>
   <Link to="/give">
      <Button w="100%" size="lg" bg={customTheme.themeColors[500]}>Da en adopci√≥n</Button>
   </Link>
    <Link to="/donate">
      <Button marginTop="10px" w="100%" size="lg" bg={customTheme.themeColors[500]}>Dona</Button>
   </Link>
   </Stack>
   </Flex>
   </Box>
  );
}

export default Home;
